{"tid":426133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾有警兼職揸的士劏客被捕","createTime":"2017-10-06T10:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T11:10:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9ef8ef9168d7c8c14641e9efc4c42caa1af294","tid":426133,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20173941&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20173941%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171006&d=DKpFC8K9Iqunn6gZfZiHKgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3eb5e5f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20173941%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20171006&h=b6d69ca2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20173941&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20171006</a><br />\n<br />\n曾有警兼職揸的士劏客被捕<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171006/large/17980625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171006%2Flarge%2F17980625.jpg&h=7f0a8d54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾有警員秘撈揸的士卻遇上警方放蛇，被揭濫收車資被即場拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】包括警察在內等公務員秘撈的個案時有發生。2012年就有高級警員趁休假兼職揸的士，豈料遇上警方放蛇，被揭發濫收一倍車資劏客，被即場拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n另一名男警同樣秘撈揸的士時衝燈與其他車輛相撞，為免被揭發後影響長俸，以3萬元引誘朋友頂包，被控妨礙司法公正。<br />\n<br />\n同年，有衝鋒隊警員因經常請假，被同袍舉報秘撈；經調查後確認指控成立，該名警員隨即到其駐守的西貢警署天台企跳，經談判專家游說下才回到安全位置，轉送九龍醫院接受精神科檢查。<br />\n<br />\n本報在2014年則揭發有衝鋒隊警員從泰國偷運俗稱「碌葛」的完整嬰屍陰牌，再在網上兜售以及偷運內地；更教唆客人如何避開X光機檢驗偷運入境，最後被警方以涉嫌「輸入人類屍體」罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁御和<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t警涉秘撈地產　自己環頭帶客睇樓慫恿僭建天台屋出租<br />\n要聞 13小時前"},{"pid":"ea3d6a4e9092e235c6d0e5cdd44d918865b3ce1b","tid":426133,"uid":111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T10:52:37.000Z","msg":"黑警祕撈做埋黑的<br />\n連副業都係偷呃拐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757cb1c08e7787c6ba08743888f5821361796a12","tid":426133,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:10:16.000Z","msg":"想揾黑警冇犯過嘅罪 同揾hello kitty冇出過嘅產品一樣難"}]}